{"tid":2237923,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傅穎低胸吊帶背心照贈網民：現在看會不會覺得好冷？","createTime":"2020-10-10T16:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T03:31:06.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ebde4d906a019ecbe5da30e054748abbe43a2ed1","tid":2237923,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"現年36歲的傅穎（Theresa）去年回港發展，觀眾最近就可以在ViuTV劇集《熟女強人》看到她的演出。不過Theresa未有忘記大陸粉絲，昨日（10/10）在微博上載多張靚相送給他們，穿上黑色低胸吊帶背心的她大曬白滑肌，並寫着：「夏天過去了，這組照片竟靜靜躺在哪沒好好發過。現在看到，會不會覺得好冷？沒關係啦，冷一下頭腦更清醒，知道要拍新照片了。」網民非常高興，紛紛留言：「青春美麗」、「好看」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201010/391608665007853568.jpeg/UYJxkibzYGYnG3GMnFSfVVUKMPciQDpuRTy3-UU8t_k?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201010%2F391608665007853568.jpeg%2FUYJxkibzYGYnG3GMnFSfVVUKMPciQDpuRTy3-UU8t_k%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=960b53de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTheresa未有忘記大陸粉絲，在微博上載多張靚相送給他們。"},{"pid":"5e9f788a995f6408226c81547d1d183c14d96855","tid":2237923,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/61ca0afagy1gjk08ey89wj237k4tche8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ca0afagy1gjk08ey89wj237k4tche8.jpg&h=080c71f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/61ca0afagy1gjk08y65brj20sh0shh2t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ca0afagy1gjk08y65brj20sh0shh2t.jpg&h=ceb0c2cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/61ca0afagy1gjk08vegzcj237k4tc1lc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F61ca0afagy1gjk08vegzcj237k4tc1lc.jpg&h=410bce8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/61ca0afagy1gjk0m0vop2j221d21dhdu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h